            <title>[PDFBOX-5769] Duplicated code in interactive.annotation.layout and interactive.form</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-5769</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I just stumbled upon lots of duplicated code in those two packages that I think should be cleaned up. As that would mean users would have to change imports, that would be a change for a major version. I will prepare a PR for this to suggest some changes that you can review and comment.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
